591
00:51:56,280 --> 00:51:58,980
I got it. Just this once.

592
00:51:58,980 --> 00:52:01,790
These people are never here when I need them.

593
00:52:01,790 --> 00:52:05,430
I'll give you a lot of allowance. Just this once.

594
00:52:05,430 --> 00:52:07,160
- A lot?
- A lot.

595
00:52:07,160 --> 00:52:09,220
You promised.

596
00:52:33,170 --> 00:52:36,620
