604
00:53:13,630 --> 00:53:16,440
- Dummy!
- What!

605
00:53:16,440 --> 00:53:18,650
Give me a coupon.

606
00:53:27,210 --> 00:53:29,060
Psycho.

607
00:53:34,270 --> 00:53:37,390
