615
00:54:26,660 --> 00:54:27,830
Coupon?

616
00:54:30,560 --> 00:54:32,980
Stop ordering now.

617
00:54:32,980 --> 00:54:34,820
Didn't I tell you?

618
00:54:34,820 --> 00:54:39,220
