619
00:54:39,220 --> 00:54:44,050
The other is collecting chicken coupons.

620
00:54:46,890 --> 00:54:49,020
Psycho.

621
00:54:49,020 --> 00:54:51,840
Psycho! Psycho!

622
00:54:52,600 --> 00:54:56,300
Collecting chicken coupons!

623
00:55:01,950 --> 00:55:05,540
