625
00:55:26,950 --> 00:55:30,760
Take. It. All. Take it all!

626
00:55:32,260 --> 00:55:37,200
If you order one more time, you're really going to die!

627
00:55:37,200 --> 00:55:40,410
I want to do that too.

628
00:55:40,410 --> 00:55:44,740
But since I collected ten, if I don't order again, it'll just go to waste.

629
00:55:44,740 --> 00:55:46,740
I'm really prudent.

630
00:55:46,740 --> 00:55:51,310
Tae Woon. Let's have a serious and honest talk.

631
00:55:51,310 --> 00:55:56,190
You hate me right? Is teasing me fun?

632
00:55:56,190 --> 00:55:57,340
Do you get excited?

633
00:55:57,340 --> 00:56:04,430
Hey. I'm not even a kid, If I tease you- it''s really fun!

634
00:56:04,430 --> 00:56:06,560
Didn't I tell you?

635
00:56:13,560 --> 00:56:15,100
Go.

636
00:56:32,050 --> 00:56:35,910
