639
00:56:58,990 --> 00:57:02,330
I told you I hate chicken.

640
00:57:02,330 --> 00:57:05,860
Yes. Please continue to hate chicken from now on.

641
00:57:05,860 --> 00:57:09,480
Don't ever order for delivery.

642
00:57:09,480 --> 00:57:11,960
