00:57:19,360 --> 00:57:22,050
You're crazy. Give it back.

645
00:57:22,050 --> 00:57:24,130
Give it back!

646
00:57:24,910 --> 00:57:27,820
'I still have ten coupons'

647
00:57:31,320 --> 00:57:36,030
Dae Hwi. I can't believe it's already our 200th day.

648
00:57:36,030 --> 00:57:37,630
I know right.

649
00:57:37,630 --> 00:57:39,310
- I'll see you later.
- Alright.

